{"tid":2356762,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"更衣室集體施壓！奧斯爾同意離開阿仙奴","createTime":"2021-01-07T04:06:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T05:22:12.000Z","uid":147522,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8a96a8d3dfa3b1a1738cb1f0c3afa68774cec319","tid":2356762,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:06:13.000Z","msg":"　　阿仙奴終於迎來了一個好消息，那就是奧斯爾（Mesut Ozil）同意在一月份離開阿仙奴。為了逼走奧斯爾，阿仙奴內部發生了很多事情。<br />\n<br />\n　　《每日郵報》透露，奧斯爾本來是想要繼續留在阿仙奴，混到夏天合約到期，將35萬英鎊週薪合約全部混完，但如今阿仙奴更衣室內出現了變化，一些有影響力的球員，支持阿迪達封殺奧斯爾的決定，這讓奧斯爾徹底死心了，他才願意在一月份離開阿仙奴。<br />\n<br />\n　　如今奧斯爾可能的下家是美國華盛頓特區聯，以及土耳其球隊費倫巴治，不過有土耳其媒體稱，奧斯爾已經和費倫巴治達成了協議。<br />\n<br />\n　　20-21賽季開始前，阿仙奴將奧斯爾踢出英超和歐霸盃大名單，新賽季開始至今，奧斯爾一直被封殺。"},{"pid":"b46e3b4c559e2691720f4c8d26236b0983968529","tid":2356762,"uid":122672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:07:50.000Z","msg":"我要返工呀，唔好阻住我"},{"pid":"e0fe5b82e265109ca2ed0d4ba6cf306d61472198","tid":2356762,"uid":122167,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QxcEMrR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxcEMrR.gif&h=3c5e283f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60e8b10b274fa200383bf162e6a278db2e7f6121","tid":2356762,"uid":39912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0fe5b82e265109ca2ed0d4ba6cf306d61472198","tid":2356762,"uid":122167,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:31:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QxcEMrR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxcEMrR.gif&h=3c5e283f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:33:52.000Z","msg":"Jumbo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89778b4ea05506d3c44bae0e0b1b3478c9b3fad0","tid":2356762,"uid":185492,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:35:40.000Z","msg":"仲以為係潮文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"